OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773411079
OL,3,CNo criminal investigations into
OL,4,Crheumatology deaths, police confirm
OL,6,FThere will be no criminal
OL,7,Finvestigation into the deaths of
OL,8,Frheumatology patients in Jersey.
OL,10,FIt comes after an investigation by the
OL,11,Fisland's police force concluded that
OL,12,Fthe threshold for gross negligence
OL,13,Fmanslaughter (GNM) has not been met.
OL,15,FConcerns were raised in July 2024 that
OL,16,Fthe deaths of at least 20 rheumatology
OL,17,Fpatients were caused directly or
OL,18,Findirectly by their care in the
OL,19,Fisland's health service.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773411079
OL,3,CNo criminal investigations into
OL,4,Crheumatology deaths, police confirm
OL,6,FIn a statement, the States of Jersey
OL,7,FPolice say: "The legal bar for GNM is
OL,8,Fextremely high and requires five
OL,9,Fspecific elements to be proven,
OL,10,Fincluding clear evidence of a serious
OL,11,Fand obvious risk of death at the time
OL,12,Fof negligently breaching a duty, and
OL,13,Fthat the actions or omissions
OL,14,Fmaterially caused or contributed to
OL,15,Fthe death to a significant degree."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
