OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773411079
OL,3,CNo criminal investigations into
OL,4,Crheumatology deaths, police confirm
OL,6,FIt follows a damning 2024 independent
OL,7,Freview into the island's Rheumatology
OL,8,FService, revealing that certain
OL,9,Fpatients had been misdiagnosed and
OL,10,Fprescribed drugs against EU and UK
OL,11,Fguidelines.
OL,13,FAt the time, the health department
OL,14,Fadmitted it was "inevitable" that some
OL,15,Fpatients "will have been harmed
OL,16,Fclinically, emotionally or
OL,17,Feconomically" as a result.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G3/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773411079
OL,3,CNo criminal investigations into
OL,4,Crheumatology deaths, police confirm
OL,6,FA separate audit also highlighted
OL,7,F"significant concerns" over the
OL,8,Fmedication given by doctors to
OL,9,Fpatients between January 2019 and
OL,10,FJanuary 2022.
OL,12,FIt found there was no appropriate
OL,13,Fevidence for 153 people to be given
OL,14,Fanti-rheumatic and anti-inflammatory
OL,15,Fdrugs, which was more than half of all
OL,16,Fthe records reviewed.
OL,18,FIn more than a third of cases, these
OL,19,Fprescriptions were stopped following
OL,20,Fface-to-face appointments.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G4/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
