OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773411079
OL,3,CNo criminal investigations into
OL,4,Crheumatology deaths, police confirm
OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News in 2024, the
OL,7,Fisland's previous Medical Director,
OL,8,FPatrick Armstrong, said: "This is the
OL,9,Fmost difficult and challenging
OL,10,Fsituation I've had to face in my 33-
OL,11,Fyear career as a doctor.
OL,13,F"I am the one who requested this
OL,14,Freview by the Royal College of
OL,15,FPhysicians. The first time issues were
OL,16,Fraised to me by a junior doctor, I
OL,17,Facted upon them, and this is where
OL,18,Fit's led to.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G5/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773411079
OL,3,CNo criminal investigations into
OL,4,Crheumatology deaths, police confirm
OL,6,F"We can only say sorry, this is a
OL,7,Fproblem that's been going on for a
OL,8,Fvery long time and came to light two
OL,9,Fand a half years ago."
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G6/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773411079
OL,3,CNo criminal investigations into
OL,4,Crheumatology deaths, police confirm
OL,6,FIn its statement, Jersey Police
OL,7,Fcontinue to explain why these cases
OL,8,Fwill not undergo criminal
OL,9,Finvestigation, adding: "After careful
OL,10,Fconsideration of expert evidence
OL,11,Fprovided by an independent
OL,12,Frheumatology specialist and legal
OL,13,Fconsultation, the States of Jersey
OL,14,FPolice have determined that the
OL,15,Fthreshold for gross negligence
OL,16,Fmanslaughter is not met, and therefore
OL,17,Fa criminal investigation will not be
OL,18,Flaunched.
OL,20,F"This decision has been reached only
OL,21,Fafter a full and detailed assessment.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G7/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BCh Is News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,387,380,120,260,000,100
PN,38608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F386A1773411079
OL,3,CNo criminal investigations into
OL,4,Crheumatology deaths, police confirm
OL,6,F"This does not lessen the seriousness
OL,7,Fof the circumstances or the impact on
OL,8,Fthose affected, and support for the
OL,9,Ffamilies continues.
OL,11,F"Although the Police assessment is
OL,12,Fcomplete, the wider process continues.
OL,13,FThe matters have now been referred to
OL,14,Fthe Viscount for consideration, who
OL,15,Fwill independently decide whether an
OL,16,Finquest is required in each case.
OL,18,F"The General Medical Council (GMC)
OL,19,Fhave been notified of the
OL,20,Fcircumstances.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G8/9
OL,2,W+.!/*%/*%/*%/*%+,"-$ /(,'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,
